<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 ">
      <div class="left-content">
        <canvas id="canvas" width="550" height="500"></canvas>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 ">
      <div class="right-content">
        <h1>Logic</h1>
        <div class="arraysDescription">

          <div class="div1">
            <p>
              <b>IF</b> and <b>ELSE</b> decides what our code does depending on what we tell it to look out for. <b>IF</b> says.... "if this thing is true, do what is on the line below. <b>ELSE</b> says... if what we said above isn't true, do the next line. </p>
            <p>
              Enter a number between 1 and 4 to call chickens to your farm:
            </p>
            <span>
              <input type="integer" id="chickenGenerate">
              <button type="button" id="getChickens">Generate chickens</button>
              <p id="error_msg"></p>
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="div2" id="farm" style="display: none;" >
            <p>The farm can only have 4 chickens at a time. try changing the number of chickens and see if you can discover how the code below works </p>
            <p>(it checks if the farm is full).  </p>

            <div class="col-sm-5">
              <p><b>IF</b> there are 4 chickens</p>
              <p>   puts "the farm is full"</p>
              <p><b>ELSE</b></p>
              <p>   puts "chickens welcome!"</p>
              <p><b>END</b></p>
              <br>
              <button type="button" id="if_button">Check if the farm is full</button>
              <br>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-7" id="feedback" style="display: none;" >
              <h1 id= "full" style= "display: none;">THE FARM IS FULL</h1>
              <h1 id= "empty" style= "display: none;">CHICKENS WELCOME</h1>
          </div>

          <div class="toggle_button">
            <%= link_to 'Play again!', pages_home_path %>
          </div>
        </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="fence">
  <img src="../images/fence3.png" alt="Fence" class="center-block" width="100%" height="60%" />
</div>

